n-missions.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/overwatch-2-illari-invasion-missions-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/overwatch-2-illari-invasion-missions-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/overwatch-2-illari-invasion-missions-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/overwatch-2-illari-invasion-missions-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/overwatch-2-illari-invasion-missions-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3481807" class="wp-caption-text"> 《守望先锋 2》图片来源：暴雪娱乐</figcaption></figure><p>“当死神说‘买、买、买’并将新英雄锁定在战斗通行证后面并取消故事模式时，我哭了。真正的有史以来的游戏，”一篇<a href="https://steamcommunity.com/profiles/76561198257048334/recommended/2357570/">评论</a>说。</p><p>上周， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/overwatch-2-update-brings-invasion-missions-and-new-hero-illari-3481805"><em>《守望先锋 2：入侵》</em>推出</a>，增加了一个新英雄、一个新模式和三个关于《守望先锋》和《归零地带》之间战斗的新叙事任务。然而，要玩这些任务，有兴趣的人<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/overwatch-2-wont-release-paid-story-missions-for-several-seasons-3464199">必须至少支付 14.99 美元购买<em>入侵</em>捆绑包</a>。</p><p>这让那些对五月<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/overwatch-2s-planned-co-op-pve-mode-scrapped-by-blizzard-3444651">取消的</a>“合作、叙事驱动的游戏体验”模式（让玩家对抗敌人）感到失望的玩家感到刺痛。此外，暴雪娱乐团队确认， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/overwatch-2-wont-release-paid-story-missions-for-several-seasons-3464199">下一批叙事任务最早要到2024年才会推出</a>。</p><p> 7月，暴雪娱乐宣布裁员<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/activision-blizzard-leaves-overwatch-league-in-the-lurch-after-layoffs-3471055">约50名电子竞技员工</a>，但<em>《守望</em>先锋联赛》专员肖恩·米勒表示，明年这款竞技游戏将“焕发全球活力”。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中，<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/the-pokemon-company">神奇宝贝公司</a>表示，为了保证粉丝的“质量” <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/the-pokemon-company-considering-slowing-its-release-schedule-down-3482589">，关于改变神奇宝贝发布频率的讨论“越来越多”</a> 。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/overwatch-2-becomes-the-worst-reviewed-game-on-steam-3482611">《守望先锋 2》成为 Steam 上评价最差的游戏</a>后，首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
